# contains(_:)

**Instance Method**

Checks if the set contains a pose with the given name.

## Declaration

```swift
func contains(_ poseID: SkeletalPose.ID) -> Bool
```

## Parameters

- **poseID**: The name of the pose to look up

## Return Value

`true` a pose with matching name is contained in the set.
